{"tid":1844903,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湖北新增新型肺炎确诊病例371宗 新增死亡24宗","createTime":"2020-01-26T23:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T00:11:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aeddddd4d22ff49a3eaf7e0c354108c79c0c4abb","tid":1844903,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:16:45.000Z","msg":"據湖北省衛生健康委員會1月27日發布消息，2020年1月26日時0-24，湖北省報告新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎新增確診病例371例，新增死亡病例24例，新增出院病例2例其中：<br />\n<br />\n潛江市首次報告確診病例，新增確診病例中，武漢市80例，黃石市5例，十堰市20例，襄陽市34例，宜昌市11例，荊州市14例，荊門市52例，鄂州市19例，孝感市45例，黃岡市32例，咸寧市21例，16隨州市例，恩施州8例，仙桃市1例，天門市8例，潛江5例;新增死亡病例中，武漢市18例，荊門市2例，孝感市1例，黃岡市2例，潛江市1例;新增出院病例中，武漢市2例。<br />\n<br />\n截至1月26日24時，湖北省累計報告新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例1423例，重症病例221例，危重症病例69例，死亡病例76例，出院病例44例。"},{"pid":"a7c1b7fcc8a8662331de94351e5888aa9459231b","tid":1844903,"uid":54511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04wHu2V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04wHu2V.jpg&h=861fbbcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a44124b95ec907cc0354c063ff0e30cc008959","tid":1844903,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:05:44.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4b0aca9f2d1f3c55504221160eb77640f1bd7b","tid":1844903,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:09:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 香港班醫護仲唔罷工只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港，間接促成社區爆發，害死更多人，包括你自己在內<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪想犧牲自己條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edG0Z6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedG0Z6X.jpg&h=8ac5b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F